Step 1:
======

Copy the data into HDFS using the below commands

	hadoop fs -mkdir /hive	
	hadoop fs -mkdir /hive/csv
	hadoop fs -mkdir /hive/csv/task7

	hadoop fs -put /home/orienit/Desktop/hive_tasks/files/Behavioral_Risk_Factor_Surveillance_System.csv /hive/csv/task7/

Note: '/home/orienit/Desktop/hive_tasks/files/Behavioral_Risk_Factor_Surveillance_System.csv' is my local path.
